            WPC Doors
          </h2>
          <p>

            WPC doors, or Wood Plastic Composite
            doors, are engineered, eco-friendly doors
            made from a mix of wood fiber,
            thermoplastics, and additives. They offer the
            aesthetic of wood with superior, long-lasting
            durability, being 100% waterproof, termiteproof, fire-resistant, and low-maintenance.
            They are ideal for high-moisture areas like
            kitchens and bathrooms.

          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="louver-composition__visual fade-up" data-delay="160">
          <a class="louver-composition__image-link" href="/assets/images/projects/wpc-doors.jpeg"
